### What the test suite covers

| Area | Tests |
|---|---|
| **Authentication** | Unauthenticated users get 401; no service/audit calls |
| **Authorisation** | Non-admin users get 403; system-admin passes through |
| **Existence check** | Unknown IDs return 404 without audit |
| **Mandatory field validation** | Each mandatory field (`title`, `body`, `org_id`) individually; blank/whitespace strings; all-missing produces multiple errors simultaneously (no fail-fast) |
| **Successful update** | 200 returned; correct args forwarded to service; service called exactly once |
| **Audit record** | Written on success; contains action, entity ID, user ID, changes, timezone-aware timestamp; written *after* persistence; omitted on every failure path |
| **Edge cases** | Optional extra fields accepted; deactivation; whitespace-only title; long values passed through unchanged; DB exceptions prevent audit write |
